# Macros:
#  P          Device Prefix
#  R          Device Suffix
#  PORT       Asyn Port name
#  TIMEOUT    Timeout
#  ADDR       Asyn Port address
#  TYPE       Asyn Type e.g. Int32
#  FTVL       Format, e.g. Int
#  NELEMENTS  Number of elements
